00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,720
但哈罗德找到了我
But Harold found me.

721
00:40:13,720 --> 00:40:15,630
那天我在公园里画画
I was painting in the park one day,

722
00:40:15,630 --> 00:40:18,070
然后  这个男人出现了
And...there was this man,

723
00:40:18,950 --> 00:40:21,630
一月天里  吃着冰淇淋
Eating an ice cream cone in January.

724
00:40:22,450 --> 00:40:24,070
冲我微笑
And he smiled at me.

725
00:40:24,610 --> 00:40:26,330
问我想不想要一个
He asked me if I wanted one.

726
00:40:31,410 --> 00:40:32,790
他跟你住在一起吗
Does he live here with you?

727
00:40:33,170 --> 00:40:34,420
不  没有
No, he doesn't.

728
00:40:34,420 --> 00:40:35,950
以前是
He used to.

729
00:40:38,530 --> 00:40:40,150
两年前我失去了他
I lost him two years ago.

730
00:40:42,630 --> 00:40:44,000
发生了一场意外
There was an accident.

731
00:40:46,580 --> 00:40:47,750
我很遗憾
I'm sorry.

732
00:41:13,490 --> 00:41:15,060
地方选得不错
Good location.

733
00:41:15,810 --> 00:41:17,030
视线清楚
Clear line of sight,

734
00:41:18,460 --> 00:41:20,950
又有足够的遮挡物和距离
but enough obstructions and distance

735
00:41:20,950 --> 00:41:22,390
防止她看到你
to avoid being seen.

736
00:41:24,780 --> 00:41:26,420
我编写了一个程序
I built an app that alerts me

737
00:41:26,420 --> 00:41:28,910
如果我和她距离一百米之内就会提醒我
if I ever get within 100 meters of her.

738
00:41:30,150 --> 00:41:32,440
我从未后悔造了那台机器
I've never regretted building the machine.

739
00:41:34,580 --> 00:41:37,180
但我以前没有充分意识到我要为此付出的代价
But I didn't fully realize the personal cost.

740
00:41:37,770 --> 00:41:39,090
我很擅长电脑
I'm good with computers.

741
00:41:40,260 --> 00:41:44,290
但人  除了格蕾斯之外
People--well, people other than Grace--

742
00:41:44,980 --> 00:41:47,090
对我来说一直是个谜
have always been a mystery to me.

743
00:41:47,550 --> 00:41:49,130
我并没意识到
I failed to recognize the lengths

744
00:41:49,130 --> 00:41:54,120
