to which they would go to protect the machine, to control it.

745
00:41:56,940 --> 00:42:01,450
当我意识到时候  对我来说  为时已晚
By the time I realized it, it was too late...for me.

746
00:42:03,820 --> 00:42:05,130
但对她还不晚
But not for her.

747
00:42:07,090 --> 00:42:08,410
你看  里瑟先生
You see, Mr. Reese,

748
00:42:09,090 --> 00:42:11,490
如果知道机器的存在是个病毒
If knowing about the machine is like a virus,

749
00:42:12,290 --> 00:42:15,340
那我就是第一感染源
that makes me patient zero.

750
00:42:15,340 --> 00:42:19,510
只是在我身边都会危及她的安全
Simply being near me was putting her life in danger.

751
00:42:23,460 --> 00:42:24,720
我很遗憾
I'm sorry.

752
00:42:25,130 --> 00:42:26,680
我已经很幸运了
I was lucky.

753
00:42:28,010 --> 00:42:30,490
我拥有四年的
I had four years of...

754
00:42:31,650 --> 00:42:33,090
幸福时光
happiness.

755
00:42:36,520 --> 00:42:38,440
有些人只有四天
Some people only get four days.

